org.gicentre.treemappa.version

Interface VersionHandler

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Ver20

    public interface VersionHandler
    Interface describing Processing version neutral versions of methods that are incompatible between Processing 1.x and 2.x.
    Version:
    3.3.0, 18th April, 2016.
    Author:
    Jo Wood, giCentre.

    • Method Detail

      • rect

        void rect(float a,
          float b,
          float c,
          float d,
          float r)
        Draws a rounded rectangle with the given position parameters a-d with corners rounded to radius r.
        Parameters:
        a - First rectangle parameter (depends on the current rectMode() setting.
        b - Second rectangle parameter (depends on the current rectMode() setting.
        c - Third rectangle parameter (depends on the current rectMode() setting.
        d - Fourth rectangle parameter (depends on the current rectMode() setting.
        r - Radius of curvature of the corners of the rectangle.
